## âš™ï¸ **ConfiguraÃ§Ã£o do Backend**

### **1. Configurar URL da API**

**Arquivo:** `js/main.js` (linha ~7)

```javascript
const API_BASE_URL = '/api';  // â¬…ï¸ ALTERAR AQUI
```

**Exemplos:**
```javascript
// Node.js/Express
const API_BASE_URL = 'http://localhost:3000/api';

// Spring Boot
const API_BASE_URL = 'http://localhost:8080/api';

// .NET
const API_BASE_URL = 'http://localhost:5000/api';

// Python/FastAPI
const API_BASE_URL = 'http://localhost:8000/api';
```

### **2. Endpoints Esperados**

#### **GET /api/courses**
Query params: `?page=1&limit=12&category=Python`

```json
{
  "data": {
    "courses": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Nome do Curso",
        "instructor": "Nome do Instrutor",
        "category": "Python",
        "rating": 4.8,
        "reviewCount": 1234,
        "price": 49.99,
        "oldPrice": 99.99,
        "thumbnail": "url-da-imagem",
        "badge": "Bestseller"
      }
    ],
    "totalPages": 5,
    "currentPage": 1,
    "totalCourses": 48
  }
}
```

#### **GET /api/categories**
```json
{
  "data": [
    "Python",
    "React",
    "Node.js",
    "Machine Learning"
  ]
}
```

#### **POST /auth/login**
```json
{
  "email": "user@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}
```

**Resposta:**
```json
{
  "data": {
    "user": {
      "name": "Nome do UsuÃ¡rio",
      "email": "user@email.com",
      "role": "STUDENT" // ou "INSTRUCTOR"
    },
    "token": "jwt-token-aqui"
  }
}
```

### **3. Configurar CORS (Backend)**

#### **Node.js/Express:**
```javascript
const cors = require('cors');
app.use(cors({
  origin: 'http://localhost:5500',
  credentials: true
}));
```

#### **Spring Boot:**
```java
@CrossOrigin(origins = "http://localhost:5500")
```

#### **.NET:**
```csharp
builder.Services.AddCors(options => {
    options.AddPolicy("AllowFrontend",
        policy => policy.WithOrigins("http://localhost:5500")
                       .AllowAnyHeader()
                       .AllowAnyMethod());
});
```

#### **Python/FastAPI:**
```python
from fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware

app.add_middleware(
    CORSMiddleware,
    allow_origins=["http://localhost:5500"],
    allow_credentials=True,
    allow_methods=["*"],
    allow_headers=["*"],
)
```

